Chhattisgarh Professional Examination Board (CGVYAPAM) is a professional examination board of Chhattisgarh, India. It conducts various tests for admission to professional courses and streams. It is the largest examination conducting body of Chhattisgarh and comes directly under the Directorate of Technical Education, Government of Chhattisgarh. The Chhattisgarh Professional Examination Board is a self-financed, autonomous body incorporated by Government of Chhattisgarh established in July 2005 to organize state level pre-admission and other examination.
